	<string name="_bx_azrcon_information_block"><![CDATA[
        <p>This module can be used to login to this site using Azure Active Directory accounts.</p>
        <p>To make it work make new registration in <a target="_blank" href="https://portal.azure.com/">Azure portal</a> then goto Azure AD B2C service. <br />
        When asked specify the following Redirect URI:<br />
            <ul>
                <li>Redirect URL: <strong>{0}</strong></li>
            </ul>
            When registration is complete go to "Overview"  to copy Application (client) ID and Directory (tenant) ID. <br /> 
            Client secret can be generated in "Certificates & secrets". <br />
            For more info please refer to <a target="_blank" href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/quickstart-register-app">official documentation</a>.
        </p>]]></string>
